## Frequency Compensation

To ensure stable operation, Miller compensation was incorporated into the design.

Compensation values were selected through analytical calculations and refined through simulation. Stability was evaluated using AC analysis and verified through phase-margin measurements.

Key design considerations included:

- Dominant pole placement
- Unity-gain bandwidth
- Phase margin
- Gain margin

