## Bias Network Optimization

A dedicated biasing network was designed to generate stable operating currents throughout the amplifier.

Multiple design iterations were performed to:

- Reduce power consumption
- Improve gain
- Increase bandwidth
- Maintain transistor saturation

Current mirror dimensions were adjusted based on simulation results to achieve the desired operating points.

